{
  "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "在一张纸上，两点之间最短的路是一条直线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "可地球是圆的，飞机从北京飞纽约，走的却是一条弯弯的弧线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "在球面上，笔直的直线并不存在，我们需要一种新的几何。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "geodesic",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "geodesic-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/geodesic-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.59,
      "size": 41472,
      "text": "过球心切开球面，得到的最大圆圈就叫大圆，比如赤道和所有经线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "geodesic",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "geodesic-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/geodesic-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "球面上两点间的最短路径，正是连接它们的那段大圆弧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "geodesic",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "geodesic-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/geodesic-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "所以大圆就是球面世界里的直线，我们叫它测地线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "anglesum",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "anglesum-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/anglesum-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "用三段大圆弧围出一个球面三角形，量一量它的三个内角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "anglesum",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "anglesum-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/anglesum-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "你会发现三角和总是大于180度，而不是平面上那个固定的180度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "anglesum",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "anglesum-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/anglesum-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "取地球八分之一那块，三个角都是直角，加起来足足270度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "excess",
      "line_id": "exc-1",
      "filename": "excess-exc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/excess-exc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "内角和超出180度的那部分，我们称为球面盈余。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "excess",
      "line_id": "exc-2",
      "filename": "excess-exc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/excess-exc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "盈余乘以半径的平方，恰好等于这个三角形的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "excess",
      "line_id": "exc-3",
      "filename": "excess-exc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/excess-exc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "三角形越大，盈余越大，几何与面积竟如此紧密相连。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "切换不同的三角形，看内角和与盈余如何随之变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "旋转地球，观察大圆弧始终是两点间那条最短的路径。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "end-1",
      "filename": "summary-end-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/summary-end-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "球面上大圆就是直线，是两点间的最短路径。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "end-2",
      "filename": "summary-end-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/summary-end-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "球面三角形内角和大于180度，盈余正比于面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "spherical-geometry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "end-3",
      "filename": "summary-end-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/spherical-geometry/summary-end-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "弯曲的空间里藏着另一套几何法则，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
